desc-de: Jeremy Scott comes correct with a new colourway of his increasingly iconic JS Logo model. The iron, black and metallic gold colourway is finished with the Kazuki signature heeltape and signature moulded sock liner.

desc-de: This one size fits all, vintage styled American football jersey by Jeremy Scott again throws down his one of a kind style for his upcoming ObyO range. desc-de: Jeremy Scott comes correct with a new colourway of his increasingly iconic JS Logo model. The upper is constructed from debossed leather in a metallic colourway, complementing the high yellow and lemon peel highlights. Further features are found in the oversized Trefoil logo tongue, JS lace jewellery, signature laser engraving and a logo sock liner. A bold statement and guaranteed head turner.

desc-de: Jeremy Scott is a progressive designer known for his outrageous, eye-catching creations. Here he takes the iconic track dress and remakes it in his inimitable style. The dress is made from an athletic tricot material and is colour blocked, with distinctive bustier influenced embroidery on the chest. Finished with the classic 3-Stripe logo taping. Main Material: 85% Polyester/15% Cotton

desc-de: Kazuki teams up with fellow sneaker heavyweights CLOT for their reinterpretation of the iconic Superstar 80s silhouette. Featuring a full mesh upper with subtle 3-Stripe contrast stitching and a vintage style logo tongue, this Shelltoe is one of the more impressive in recent memory. The black, off white and metallic silver colourway is finished with a Kazuki signature heeltape and moulded sock liner. Essential.

desc-de: The union of James Bond, founder of Undftd, and football style icon David Beckham as the latest ObyO collaborators has thrown up an interesting, well-considered range that is sure to be highly sought after. Constructed from luxury distressed leather, this unique take on the classic Americana Mid features a heavy buckle inspired by biker boots with zippers that allow the height to be adjusted. Finished with a signature David Beckham leather sock liner.

desc-de: Kazuki Kuraishi is one of the most influential fashion designers in the street wear scene today. Hailing from Tokyo, Kazuki's influence is far reaching and his work for the ObyO collection has been universally hailed. This take on the Campus 80 is a collaboration between Kazuki and Mintos. The iconic silhouette is constructed from soft pigskin suede leather and features subtle 3-Stripe perforated branding. The iron, black and metallic gold colourway is finished with the Kazuki signature heeltape and signature moulded sock liner.

desc-de: This one size fits all, vintage styled American football jersey by Jeremy Scott again throws down his one of a kind style for his upcoming ObyO range. Redesigned for the centre stage, the jersey is adorned with contrasting rhinestones that complement the collegiate royal and white colourway.
